  "intent": "Perform SuperScript III reverse transcription qRT-PCR preparation by combining 2x RT reaction mix and enzyme mix in specified ratios (10\u00b5L + 2\u00b5L per sample plus 10\u00b5L excess), dispensing 12\u00b5L of master mix to thermocycler plate wells 33-n, adding variable volumes of RNA samples from CSV input with 5x mixing at 20\u00b5L volume, executing thermocycler profile (25\u00b0C/10min, 50\u00b0C/30min, 85\u00b0C/5min), adding 1\u00b5L RNase H, incubating at 37\u00b0C/20min, then diluting with 60\u00b5L nuclease-free water per well",
